title: (Psx) Disney's The Lion King II - Simba's Mighty Adventure [Pal]
description:
Language: English

An arcade game created based on the animated film The Lion King, who charmed the world several years ago. The game contains no violence, and there is also quite difficult, so older and younger players will also find something for themselves. The player takes on the next level (there are 10) in various forms of cartoons, but most often it is Simba (first young adult later). To access levels to jump on the palms, avoid hyena (sometimes fight with them), perform stunts, and more.
